{"tid":741354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【科技戰】華為全方位AI大計曝光 命名「達文西計劃」","createTime":"2018-07-13T14:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T04:06:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"85bce95bebf84efd5000d240f335cf00581a9065","tid":741354,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"【科技戰】華為全方位AI大計曝光 命名「達文西計劃」<br />\n<br />\n《The Information》引述消息人士透露，華為最高管理層與員工討論如何將AI融入於所有華為的產品，由基站、雲端資料中心以至手機等等，計劃取名&quot;Project Da Vinci&quot;，部分高層稱之為「D計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n達文西計劃的存在從來未被報道過，但可能對於華為產品將來帶來重大影響，其中包括發展華為最新AI晶片，再以程式透過聲音及影像去確認雲端上的資料，不過，這計劃亦可能觸動美國政府的神經。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，華為透過「D計劃」，試圖擺脫對於處理器公司Nvidia的倚賴。<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180713&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58436733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180713%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58436733&d=ceD5UE%2FeaeY398%2BLRcCkaf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2f1d64d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180713%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58436733&h=7fa15b9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180713&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58436733</a>"},{"pid":"560e3de114a3a783d2f3489dddd15b81c74d6cce","tid":741354,"uid":1989,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/230124_19c4db7cf466979f2714948fa65d3060.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F230124_19c4db7cf466979f2714948fa65d3060.png&h=a7fc21f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67d4de60852a157ffcc9b8c91fb251e4c515feb1","tid":741354,"uid":52215,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/230136_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src